\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/performance-\u0026amp;-fuel-economy\"\u003ePerformance \u0026amp; Fuel Economy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/verdict\"\u003eVerdict\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/tech-specs\"\u003eTech Specs\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982\"\u003eIntroduction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/design-\u0026amp;-features\"\u003eDesign \u0026amp; Features\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/ride-and-handling\"\u003eRide and handling\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/performance-\u0026amp;-fuel-economy\"\u003ePerformance \u0026amp; Fuel Economy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/verdict\"\u003eVerdict\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982/tech-specs\"\u003e Tech Specs \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"scrolled_div_432982\" href=\"https://www.autocarindia.com/bike-reviews/tvs-apache-rtr-310-road-test-review-432982\"\u003e\u003carticle\u003e\u003cp\u003eA number of small updates increase the biggest Apache’s appeal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePublished on Sep 30, 2024 07:00:00 AM\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"sync1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"TVS Apache RTR 310 price, performance, mileage, comfort\" title=\"TVS Apache RTR 310 road test, review\" fetchpriority=\"high\" src=\"https://cdni.autocarindia.com/Utils/ImageResizer.ashx?n=https://cdni.autocarindia.com/ExtraImages/20240926110155_R1.jpg\u0026amp;w=700\u0026amp;c=1\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"TVS Apache RTR 310 price, performance, mileage, comfort\" title=\"TVS Apache RTR 310 road test, review\" src=\"https://cdni.autocarindia.com/Utils/ImageResizer.ashx?n=https://cdni.autocarindia.com/ExtraImages/20240926110918_R2.jpg\u0026amp;w=700\u0026amp;c=1\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch6\u003eWe Like\u003c/h6\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eRide comfort, energetic performance\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eGrippy tyres, strong brakes\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eStyle, extensive features list\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch6\u003eWe Don\u0026#39;t Like\u003c/h6\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eTop model and optional extras are pricey\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eStill buzzy, prone to stalling\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen we rode the TVS Apache RTR 310 in Thailand last year, we had some complaints, which the company has now addressed via its ‘Carecraft’ service camp. Much to my chagrin, we did not experience the updated RTR 310 on dry, well-paved Thai roads. Instead, the setting was Mumbai during the peak of monsoon, which is when the roads start to go the way of the Dodo. To be fair, a bike tackling such roads in torrential rain is one of the best litmus tests there is, so let’s dive in. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"tagged-articles-container-432982\"\u003e\u003cul id=\"tab-id-432982\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca id=\"tab-vidhref-id-432982\" href=\"#.\" rel=\"#tab-videos-container-43298